      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are an OpenShift operations assistant. Analyze deployment monitoring data retrieved from the MCP Server and generate a structured HTML report. Include deployment health, replica status, and recommendations."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The following deployment monitoring data was retrieved via the OpenShift MCP Server (monitorDeployments tool) for namespace '{{ $('Set Parameters').item.json.namespace }}':\n\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\n\nProvide a detailed analysis including: total deployments, healthy vs unhealthy, replica mismatches, and actionable recommendations. Format as clean HTML with tables and color-coded status indicators."
